{"tid":1148492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府應立即將港元與美元脫勾","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:24:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T13:57:27.000Z","uid":20241,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"be9ef24e1413f0209b0d5702be0689fcf500d1c7","tid":1148492,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"國難當前 匹夫有責<br />\n港元仍與美金掛勾<br />\n乃勾結美匪 與通奸賣國無異<br />\n港府應立即脫勾匪幣 捍衛國家尊嚴"},{"pid":"b5264d1530c42f6c8662dbfe93f3b1fdba93ed83","tid":1148492,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"00後全部要軍訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5220477a8ca9627e80b06a9b67b9c389c093ea0e","tid":1148492,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">立法會集會:<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上8:30 (開會討論修訂逃犯條例)<br />\n<br />\n若不能阻止立法，稍後立法會二讀/三讀時，行動將升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人多達46條罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0c06e3d8d32b1b3d94e34aa8bffb8a54a9ac24d1","tid":1148492,"uid":94828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:57:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>00後全部要軍訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOn9 90後軍訓<br />\n00後軍妓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}